text: ��To add a SMS to favourites list just press bright yellow 'Star' icon next to the Message. Press it again to remove it from favortie How to add SMS to favourites? ��In Messages app you can share your favourite Messages in Facebook SMS and more. From Messages page press the share button on top and select Facebook. You will see a login window where you can enter your login credentionals and share the SM How can I share Messages? ��Please make sure that the app is installed on your device's internal memory.
